NK009(ta)006:0: snyan brgyud phur pa'i smad las dug phur nag po zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK009(ta)006:1: badz+ra ku m+aa ra na mo /
NK009(ta)006:2: snyan brgyud phur pa'i smad las dug phur nag po
NK009(ta)006:3: dang 'brel ba'i rjes rim tshogs kyi mchod pa ni
NK009(ta)006:4: / 'byor ldan yo byad kyi tshogs bzang zhing gya nom phud ma nyams par bshams te /
NK009(ta)006:5: badz+ra a mri ta kun+d+ha l+ai ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:6: ces bdag la gtor bas ting nge 'dzin mi gsal
NK009(ta)006:7: ba dang cho ga ma tshangs ba yod pa bsang
NK009(ta)006:8: / yang a mri tas mched lcam la ma dag la yod pa dang /
NK009(ta)006:9: yang a mri tas gtor bas tshogs rdzas kyi ma dag pa dag par bsam mo //
NK009(ta)006:12: snod kyi thod pa stong gsum khyon //
NK009(ta)006:13: bcud kyi tshogs rdzas phur bus gtams //
NK009(ta)006:15: yam las rlung byung bag chags gtor //
NK009(ta)006:16: kham las chu byung gnyis 'dzin bkrus //
NK009(ta)006:18: bdag nyid dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK009(ta)006:19: yi ge 'bru gsum char du bab //
NK009(ta)006:20: gyis shel ltar dwangs pa la //
NK009(ta)006:22: h'u gis sngo bsang mkha' ltar dag /
NK009(ta)006:23: de nyid rnam gsum 'dres pa'i steng //
NK009(ta)006:24: ma las nyi ma rab gsal ba //
NK009(ta)006:25: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor steng //
NK009(ta)006:27: skyes pa'i rigs kyi yab lnga dang //
NK009(ta)006:28: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams las /
NK009(ta)006:29: dbyings phyug yum dang bcas pa rnams //
NK009(ta)006:31: thig le byang chub sems su zhu //
NK009(ta)006:32: spris ma du chags pa las //
NK009(ta)006:34: +aahmh'u ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aih spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK009(ta)006:36: srid pa phur bur sgrub pa dang //
NK009(ta)006:37: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)006:38: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK009(ta)006:40: sras dang sprul pa khra thabs bcas //
NK009(ta)006:41: bka' nyan dam can srung ma'i tshogs //
NK009(ta)006:42: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK009(ta)006:43: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub phyir //
NK009(ta)006:44: longs spyod tshogs la gshegs su gsol //
NK009(ta)006:45: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK009(ta)006:48: bla ma dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK009(ta)006:49: yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang //
NK009(ta)006:50: gnas gsum ma mo mkha' 'gro dang //
NK009(ta)006:51: dpa' bo dpa' mor bcas pa rnams //
NK009(ta)006:52: kun bzang mchod sprin rol par mdzod //
NK009(ta)006:53: bdag gis g.yo med gus ldan pas //
NK009(ta)006:54: rnal 'byor gsang ba'i mchod pa ni //
NK009(ta)006:55: snang srid chos dang rgyal srid bdun //
NK009(ta)006:56: phyag rgya bzhi dang nyon mongs lnga //
NK009(ta)006:57: ting 'dzin mchod pa bdud rtsi lnga //
NK009(ta)006:58: 'dod yon lha mo glu dang gar //
NK009(ta)006:59: rtog med don gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK009(ta)006:60: pho brang bzhugs gnas zhing khams su //
NK009(ta)006:61: mchod pa'i sprin gyis gtibs shing rgyas //
NK009(ta)006:62: snang srid mchod par bsngo ba ni /
NK009(ta)006:64: ye shes rol pa'i zhal chen por //
NK009(ta)006:65: snod bcud ma lus mchod par sbyor //
NK009(ta)006:66: dbyings ye rol pa'i mchod pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)006:67: khams gsum thams cad mchod par 'bul //
NK009(ta)006:68: de nas kun tu dbye ba med pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)006:70: rgyal ba ma lus zhi kho'i sku //
NK009(ta)006:71: dwangs snyigs mi byed mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK009(ta)006:72: dug gsum skyon bral dbyings kyis mchod //
NK009(ta)006:74: de nas thams cad mnyam pa nyid du mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)006:75: nga dang bdag med mkha' ltar dag /
NK009(ta)006:76: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa las //
NK009(ta)006:77: gnyis med bde chen mnyam pas mchod //
NK009(ta)006:78: mnyam nyid blang dor med par rol //
NK009(ta)006:79: de nas 'dod yon gyi mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)006:81: byang chub rol pa longs spyod sprul pa'i sku //
NK009(ta)006:82: 'dod pa'i yon tan lha mo'i mchod pa 'di //
NK009(ta)006:83: snang srid ma lus 'dod dgur bsgyur byas te //
NK009(ta)006:84: mkha' ltar dag pa'i dbyings su ye shes rol //
NK009(ta)006:85: ma h+aa ga na tsakra kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:86: ma h+aa dza gad la kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:87: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:89: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:91: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:92: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:93: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:94: ma h+aa sarba p+au dza hoh de nas bar bshags ni /
NK009(ta)006:96: ye shes lha la rnam rtog mi mnga' yang //
NK009(ta)006:97: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i dam can rnams //
NK009(ta)006:98: mi yi skyon mthong tsam nas bar chad rtsom //
NK009(ta)006:99: 'gal 'khrul nongs pa ci mchis mthol lo bshags //
NK009(ta)006:100: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK009(ta)006:103: mdun du e las gnam lcags kyi brub khung phyi
NK009(ta)006:104: nag la nang lcags bsregs dmar zang nge ba kha
NK009(ta)006:105: yangs pa gting zab pa phyi na zhe sdang gi
NK009(ta)006:106: me 'bar ba / nang na gti mug gi mun pa gtibs pa /
NK009(ta)006:107: logs la nga rgyal gyi mtshon cha gzing ba /
NK009(ta)006:108: gting na 'dod chags kyi khrag mtsho dmar nag tu 'khrugs pa /
NK009(ta)006:109: phyogs kun tu phrag dog gi rlung dmar 'tshubs pa'i nang du nyams pa can dngos su gsal te /
NK009(ta)006:110: las byed sprul pa'i pho nya mang po 'gugs sgrol
NK009(ta)006:111: gyi shan pa gsod gcod kyi las la rngams shing
NK009(ta)006:112: 'khrugs nas nyi zer gyi rdul 'tshubs pa bzhin g.yo
NK009(ta)006:113: bar mos te / dang po rig 'dzin rnams bskul te /
NK009(ta)006:115: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK009(ta)006:116: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK009(ta)006:117: rig 'dzin rnams kyi dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:118: phur bu sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig u rgyan pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis //
NK009(ta)006:119: rgya gar tsan+dana nags tshal du //
NK009(ta)006:120: ji ltar rtags bstan bsnyen lam 'tshal //
NK009(ta)006:121: phur bu sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK009(ta)006:122: pan chen bi ma mi tra yis //
NK009(ta)006:123: rgya gar chu bo gang+g+aa la //
NK009(ta)006:124: ji ltar rtags bstan phur bu sgrub pa'i bal po sh+ai la many+dzu yis //
NK009(ta)006:125: man+da la yi mkhar gong du //
NK009(ta)006:126: ji ltar rtags bstan phur bu sgrub pa'i mkha' 'gro ye shes mtsho rgyal gyis //
NK009(ta)006:127: srog bdag sprul pa spyang ku la //
NK009(ta)006:128: ji ltar rtags bstan phur bu sgrub pa'i gzungs ma a tsar+ya sa le yis //
NK009(ta)006:129: nyon mongs skye shi'i chu bo la //
NK009(ta)006:130: ji ltar rtags bstan phur bu sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin pad+ma las 'brel gyis //
NK009(ta)006:131: dam sri 'tshubs pa'i dmag dpung la //
NK009(ta)006:132: ji ltar rtags bstan phur bu sgrub pa'i nye brgyud ltar ram /
NK009(ta)006:133: yang na ring brgyud ltar na /
NK009(ta)006:134: mchims ston sh+aakya pra b+ha yis //
NK009(ta)006:135: yar lung gad kyi brag phug tu //
NK009(ta)006:136: ji ltar phur bu shud pu dpal gyi seng+ge yis //
NK009(ta)006:137: 'u shang rdo mdo yi zhes snang dpyad /
NK009(ta)006:139: ji ltar phur bu sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms kyis //
NK009(ta)006:140: has po ri yi yang gong du //
NK009(ta)006:141: ji ltar phur bu mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug gis //
NK009(ta)006:142: rtsibs kyi spyang ku sngon po la //
NK009(ta)006:143: ji ltar phur bu mi yang snang /
NK009(ta)006:144: mi nub rgyal po snying po yis //
NK009(ta)006:145: bdud kyi sprul pa'i bya rog la //
NK009(ta)006:146: ji ltar phur bu lo ts+aa dpal gyi blo gros kyis //
NK009(ta)006:147: mon dmag mang po cham la phab //
NK009(ta)006:148: ji ltar phur bu ngam 'brel klu yi rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK009(ta)006:149: dgra la btab pas bgegs kyang bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:150: ji ltar phur bu ngam 'bre sa le dbang phyug gis //
NK009(ta)006:151: 'od la btab pas dkor bdag bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:152: ji ltar phur bu lang lab byang chub rdo rje yis //
NK009(ta)006:153: rkun ma'i rjes btab nor rnams khug /
NK009(ta)006:154: ji ltar phur bu sna nam shes rab tshul khrims kyis //
NK009(ta)006:155: mthu chen stag ram mi dgu bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:156: ji ltar phur bu skyi nag byang chub rin chen gyis //
NK009(ta)006:157: gyang la btab pas sku dgra bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:158: ji ltar phur bu nyang nag dbang gi shes rab kyis //
NK009(ta)006:159: dgra bgegs ma lus cham la phab //
NK009(ta)006:160: ji ltar phur bu de sras sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK009(ta)006:161: 'dar nag rta pa bcu dgu bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:162: ji ltar phur bu slob dpon drag po chen po yis //
NK009(ta)006:163: sku dgra ban+de bcu gsum bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:164: ji ltar phur bu khri rgyal zhes snang dpyad /
NK009(ta)006:165: se ston khro rgyal rdo rje yis //
NK009(ta)006:166: dgra bgegs gnyis po dus gcig bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:167: ji ltar phur bu slob ma lha rje phur ston gyis //
NK009(ta)006:168: dgra bgegs gnyis la phur pas thebs //
NK009(ta)006:169: ji ltar phur bu rgya ston nam mkha' rgyal po yis //
NK009(ta)006:170: dgra bgegs gnyis la phur pas thebs //
NK009(ta)006:171: ji ltar phur bu de'i sras nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK009(ta)006:172: dgra dang bgegs gnyis phye mar byas //
NK009(ta)006:173: ji ltar phur bu nyang ban shu mngas lung pa yis //
NK009(ta)006:174: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs phur pas bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:175: ji ltar phur bu sngags 'chang nag po pan+di tas //
NK009(ta)006:176: zhing bcu thams cad gtan la phab //
NK009(ta)006:177: ji ltar phur bu slob dpon chu bar nyang phug pas //
NK009(ta)006:178: bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin dngos grub bsnyes //
NK009(ta)006:179: ji ltar phur bu ban grogs gsang sngags rdo rje yis //
NK009(ta)006:180: thun gtor me 'bar dgra bgegs bsgral //
NK009(ta)006:181: ji ltar nyi phug ces kyang mthong /
NK009(ta)006:183: phur bu u rgyan rdo rje seng+ge yis //
NK009(ta)006:184: phur pa 'phar zhing bzhad par bsgrubs //
NK009(ta)006:185: ji ltar phur bu rig 'dzin pad+ma las 'brel gyis //
NK009(ta)006:186: dam sri 'tshubs pa'i dmag dpung la //
NK009(ta)006:187: ji ltar phur bu phur pa'i brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams //
NK009(ta)006:188: rang rang so so'i sgrub khang nas //
NK009(ta)006:189: ji ltar phur bu khyed rnams phrin las dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:190: rtags mtshan ston pa'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:191: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:192: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK009(ta)006:193: de nas 'gugs pa'i phyir thugs dam bskul zhing /
NK009(ta)006:196: srid pa phur par sgrub pa dang //
NK009(ta)006:197: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)006:198: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK009(ta)006:199: ye shes khro bo gshegs nas kyang //
NK009(ta)006:200: rtags dang mtsham ma bstan pa dang //
NK009(ta)006:201: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub grub stsol //
NK009(ta)006:202: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:203: rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs dam bskul //
NK009(ta)006:204: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:205: khro bcu yab yum thugs dam bskul //
NK009(ta)006:206: phyag brnyan chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:207: khra thabs nyi shu'i thugs dam bskul //
NK009(ta)006:208: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:209: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:210: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:211: khyed kyi phrin las dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:212: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:214: de nas gzugs la dbab cing dgug pa la drug las /
NK009(ta)006:215: dang po lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu rnams thogs te /
NK009(ta)006:217: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK009(ta)006:218: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK009(ta)006:219: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK009(ta)006:220: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK009(ta)006:221: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK009(ta)006:222: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK009(ta)006:223: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK009(ta)006:224: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK009(ta)006:225: lus ngag rdul du bshigs nas kyang //
NK009(ta)006:226: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)006:227: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya //
NK009(ta)006:228: dzahmh'u pam hohka tam ka ye /
NK009(ta)006:230: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK009(ta)006:231: ma ra se na pra mar ta na ye /
NK009(ta)006:232: dgra bgegs sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:233: ces dgra bgegs kyi bla khug pas bzlas nas /
NK009(ta)006:234: de nas gnyis pa lha dang dbral ba ni gu gul gyis bdug la /
NK009(ta)006:236: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:237: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK009(ta)006:238: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK009(ta)006:239: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar bya //
NK009(ta)006:240: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la nas /
NK009(ta)006:241: ma ra se na pra mar ta na ye ha
NK009(ta)006:242: sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aihdan+da h'u phata
NK009(ta)006:244: gsum pa gzugs la dbab pa ni yungs kar thogs la /
NK009(ta)006:246: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:247: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dngos grub bar chad gdug cing
NK009(ta)006:248: sdang sems gtogs shig grogs dang phob cig rnam par
NK009(ta)006:249: gzir bar gyis // bzhi snying dang /
NK009(ta)006:250: a be sha ya a be sha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:251: bzhi pa byad du gzhug pa ni byad thag thogs la bcing ste /
NK009(ta)006:253: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:254: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dngos grub bar chad gdug cing sdang sems zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK009(ta)006:256: sh+ai g+h+ram a na ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:257: lnga pa smyor gzhug pa ni dug thun thogs la /
NK009(ta)006:259: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:260: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dngos grub bar chad gdug cig sdang sems rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK009(ta)006:262: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:263: drug pa phung po rdul du bshigs pa la tho bas brdung ba ni tho ba thogs te /
NK009(ta)006:265: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:266: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dngos grub bar chad gdug cing sdang sems lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du bshigs //
NK009(ta)006:268: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:269: mi bzad pa'i phur pa drug btab pa la /
NK009(ta)006:271: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:272: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dngos grub bar chad gdug cing sdang sems nga yi dbang du gyur nas ni //
NK009(ta)006:273: bsgo ba'i bka' la nyan par gyis //
NK009(ta)006:275: b+hin d+ha ya b+hin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:276: dam can gyi phur pa thogs te /
NK009(ta)006:278: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:279: sprul pa chen po'i phyag brnyan chen mo'i shwa na
NK009(ta)006:280: mu kha'i sa bdag bswe mo'i bdag nyid chen mo'i
NK009(ta)006:281: khyed kyi dam tshig lus ngag rdul du bshigs nas
NK009(ta)006:282: kyang // sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)006:283: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya pa ra big+h+n+aana h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:284: ch+gee mo sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:287: g+h+ri h+na g+h+ri h+na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:288: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:290: de nas thun dbab pa ni khro bcu'i phur pa btab nas /
NK009(ta)006:292: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK009(ta)006:293: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK009(ta)006:294: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK009(ta)006:295: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK009(ta)006:296: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK009(ta)006:297: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK009(ta)006:298: h'u ma ma pa sham ku ru ma ti nyaya
NK009(ta)006:299: ka ra i nan d+ha ti ma ma sh+ai g+h+ram
NK009(ta)006:300: ka ra ye sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:301: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK009(ta)006:303: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK009(ta)006:304: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:305: badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan+da h'u /
NK009(ta)006:306: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:307: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK009(ta)006:308: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:309: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK009(ta)006:311: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai wa h'u /
NK009(ta)006:312: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:313: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK009(ta)006:315: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK009(ta)006:317: badz+ra kro d+ha tre lokya bi dza ya h'u /
NK009(ta)006:319: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK009(ta)006:320: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:321: ces khro bcu'i sngags kyi thun brab bo //
NK009(ta)006:322: de nas sras phur snying dkar nag mtshams su btab ste /
NK009(ta)006:324: srid pa phur par sgrub pa dang //
NK009(ta)006:325: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)006:326: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:327: sprul pa chen po'i phyag brnyan chen mo'i shwa na
NK009(ta)006:328: mu kha'i sa bdag chen mo'i khyed kyi dam tshig
NK009(ta)006:329: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs
NK009(ta)006:330: kyis // gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK009(ta)006:331: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK009(ta)006:332: lus ngag rdul du bshigs nas kyang //
NK009(ta)006:333: sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba mdzod //
NK009(ta)006:334: bzhi snying dang spu gri'i sngags kyis bsgral te /
NK009(ta)006:335: de nas gtun du brdung te /
NK009(ta)006:337: brdung shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK009(ta)006:338: bka' las 'da' byed sdig chen rnams //
NK009(ta)006:339: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK009(ta)006:340: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK009(ta)006:341: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK009(ta)006:342: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK009(ta)006:343: lha yang rung ste brlag par gyur //
NK009(ta)006:344: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh ch+gee m+aa ra ya /
NK009(ta)006:345: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya /
NK009(ta)006:347: ma ra se na pra marta na ye sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:353: 'bar ba chen po'i zhal hom du //
NK009(ta)006:354: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK009(ta)006:355: ngas bstabs khyed kyi yul la rol //
NK009(ta)006:356: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa rnams //
NK009(ta)006:357: lhag ma med par bzhes nas kyang //
NK009(ta)006:358: dgra bgegs bag chags kun byang shog /
NK009(ta)006:359: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh b+hin+d+ha ya b+hin+d+ha ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:362: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:367: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK009(ta)006:369: a b+hi tsar+ya'i dus la bab pa'i brnag pa'o //
NK009(ta)006:370: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya nyer gcig bazla'o //
NK009(ta)006:371: brnag pa de kho na la'o //
NK009(ta)006:372: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya lan bco brgyad bazla'o //
NK009(ta)006:374: k+ai la ya lan bdun bazla'o //
NK009(ta)006:379: de nas las kyi mtha' mnan pa byed par 'dod na /
NK009(ta)006:380: brub khung nang du ling+ga spyi'am dgra sri g.yag mgo sogs gang 'dod sbyar te /
NK009(ta)006:382: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK009(ta)006:383: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob ba'i //
NK009(ta)006:384: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK009(ta)006:385: gnod cing gdug pa'i ch+gee dgra sri sogs 'di //
NK009(ta)006:386: stobs chen khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK009(ta)006:387: byang chub sems ni ma skyes par //
NK009(ta)006:388: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK009(ta)006:393: s+t+wam b+ha ya ch+gee m+aa ra ya nan /
NK009(ta)006:395: de nas dug gtor steng du blugs te /
NK009(ta)006:401: zhes mtshon cha'i char dbab par bsam mo //
NK009(ta)006:402: de nas g.yam par rdo rje rgya gram bris pas kha bcad /
NK009(ta)006:404: lam sogs kyi ri rab kyis mnan par bsam /

NK009(ta)006:406: cig gis lha rnams bskyed la lha'i pho brang btab
NK009(ta)006:407: par bsam mo // rjes su mi shis pa'i gnas su phyin la /
NK009(ta)006:411: de nas dong gru gsum du brus par thod ngan nang du ling+ga stsal la dong du sba'o //
NK009(ta)006:412: de nas zlog pa'i phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK009(ta)006:414: phur pa rol pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK009(ta)006:415: mthing nag e yi gzhal yas khang //
NK009(ta)006:416: lha chen nyi zla pad+ma'i steng //
NK009(ta)006:417: che mchog rdo rje gzhon nu che //
NK009(ta)006:418: dpal chen yak+sha he ru ka /
NK009(ta)006:419: ye shes sku mchog rigs kun bdag /
NK009(ta)006:420: h'u dang phata kyi sgra chen sgrogs //
NK009(ta)006:421: mi dmigs spros bral thugs dang ldan //
NK009(ta)006:422: dbyings las byin rlabs khro bcur sprul //
NK009(ta)006:423: chos dbyings mi 'gyur sku mdog mthing //
NK009(ta)006:424: 'jigs pa'i dur khrod dpal chas rdzogs //
NK009(ta)006:425: g.yas dkar chos sku mngon sum ston //
NK009(ta)006:426: g.yon dmar dbang drag phrin las mdzad //
NK009(ta)006:427: phrin las thams cad lhun gyis grub //
NK009(ta)006:428: skye shi rtsad gcod mche ba gtsigs //
NK009(ta)006:430: nyon mongs log lta mtha' dag 'dul //
NK009(ta)006:431: gar dgu'i nyams kyis 'jigs mdzad cing //
NK009(ta)006:432: rdo rje rtse dgus rtog pa 'joms //
NK009(ta)006:433: rtse lngas rgyud lnga gnas su 'joms //
NK009(ta)006:434: me dpung 'khor ba'i bag chags bsregs /
NK009(ta)006:435: kha t+w+aam bdud bzhi thal bar brlag /
NK009(ta)006:436: ri rab phur pas 'gal byed sgrol //
NK009(ta)006:437: che btsan dpe med 'gran zla bral //
NK009(ta)006:438: ye shes rtsal shugs stobs dang ldan //
NK009(ta)006:439: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK009(ta)006:440: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la //
NK009(ta)006:441: ban bon rbod gtong sbyor ba yi //
NK009(ta)006:442: gtad du bcug na gtad sprug cig /
NK009(ta)006:443: byad du bcug na byad thag gcod //
NK009(ta)006:444: thun du bcug na thun khang shig /
NK009(ta)006:445: khram la btab na khram kha bzlog /
NK009(ta)006:446: byad kha chom la byad ma song //
NK009(ta)006:447: byad thag chod la byad rgya shig /
NK009(ta)006:448: byad kyi tha ram bkrol du gsol //
NK009(ta)006:449: dus min 'chi rkyen ngan la zlog /
NK009(ta)006:450: byad ma rang gshed rang la phob //
NK009(ta)006:451: byad ma'i rang byad rang la bskor //
NK009(ta)006:452: byad ma rang mthu rang la zlog /
NK009(ta)006:453: zlog cig bsgyur cig mthu ma chung //
NK009(ta)006:454: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK009(ta)006:455: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh ka tam ka ye /
NK009(ta)006:457: ya tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK009(ta)006:458: ma ra se na pra marta na ye dgra bgegs sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)006:461: gnyis med sbyor ba'i yum mchog ni //
NK009(ta)006:463: sgrol yum e ka dz+aa ti gnyis //
NK009(ta)006:464: pad+ma gar gyi mkha' klong na //
NK009(ta)006:465: bee d+aur sngon po'i sku mdog 'tsher //
NK009(ta)006:466: mthing gi ral pa gcig tu 'khyil //
NK009(ta)006:467: khro gnyer rngam pa'i mche ba gcig /
NK009(ta)006:468: me lce 'od kyi phreng bas brgyan //
NK009(ta)006:469: sha rus gsol ba'i rkan sgra can //
NK009(ta)006:470: mi mgo'i phreng ba sbrul chun 'phyang //
NK009(ta)006:471: zhing chen g.yang gzhis stod g.yogs shing //
NK009(ta)006:472: gzig gi spags pa'i sham thabs can //
NK009(ta)006:473: khrag 'dzag thod rlon shin tu mdzes //
NK009(ta)006:475: 'khor lo rtse gsum g.yas na thogs //
NK009(ta)006:476: thon rlon klad khrag 'dres pa g.yon //
NK009(ta)006:477: gzir mnan drag po dpal gyi yum //
NK009(ta)006:478: thams cad dbang sdud sring gcig ma //
NK009(ta)006:479: me bza' ma la brag byon ma //
NK009(ta)006:480: srid gsum phung byed mthu mo che //
NK009(ta)006:481: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //

NK009(ta)006:487: zhal gsum phyag drug 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK009(ta)006:488: zhabs bzhis tshangs pa pho mo gnon //
NK009(ta)006:489: ri rab phur pas spyi nas gnon //
NK009(ta)006:490: sgra 'byin yum dang gnyis su med //
NK009(ta)006:491: phyogs bcur mgyogs pa'i pho nya 'gyed //

NK009(ta)006:493: g.yas g.yon rdo rje phur pa 'dril //

NK009(ta)006:643: kha gdangs mig bgrad 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK009(ta)006:644: rkan sgra 'brug sgra chems se chem //
NK009(ta)006:645: mche ba gangs ri bsnol 'dra yis //
NK009(ta)006:646: byad ma'i sha khrag rngam zas byed //
NK009(ta)006:647: de la lcags kyi mi mos zhon //
NK009(ta)006:648: lcags kyi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK009(ta)006:650: khrag gi char pa dmar po 'bebs //

NK009(ta)006:656: 'byung ba'i rgya la las bcol bas //
NK009(ta)006:657: sa la sdebs shor mnan gtad zlog /

NK009(ta)006:660: rlung la 'khor lo bskor ba zlog /

NK009(ta)006:662: byad rgya shig la byad phur phyung //
NK009(ta)006:663: thun khang shig la tha ram khrol //
NK009(ta)006:664: ban bon bsam sbyor log pa yi //
NK009(ta)006:665: phra men gdug pa'i ngan sngags zlog /
NK009(ta)006:666: zlog bsgyur drag po'i phrin las mdzod //

NK009(ta)006:671: gser gyi 'phar ba lce brgyad ma //

NK009(ta)006:683: byad gdon g.yul ngo bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK009(ta)006:684: sha khrag gtor ma sogs 'gres so //
NK009(ta)006:688: nam ni srod kyi pho nya mo //

NK009(ta)006:692: mjug ma lcags kyi sog le can //

NK009(ta)006:694: spu ni spu gri'i so dang 'dra //
NK009(ta)006:695: sder mo lcags kyu me stag 'phro //
NK009(ta)006:696: bang ni rlung gi bskyod du med //
NK009(ta)006:697: skad nistonga gsum khyab par sgrogs //

NK009(ta)006:701: g.yas pa'i rdo rjes ri rab bsnyil //

NK009(ta)006:708: nam ni srod kyi pho nya mo //

NK009(ta)006:711: ngus pa'i mchi ma ser chen 'grom //
NK009(ta)006:712: zug pa'i skad kyis lha srin brgyal //
NK009(ta)006:713: mche bas ri rab dum bur gtub //

NK009(ta)006:715: de la zhon pa'i pho nya mo //

NK009(ta)006:722: khyi gdong dmar nag dgra la rngam //
NK009(ta)006:727: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)006:728: nam ni gung gi dam can ma //
NK009(ta)006:729: dpal ldan lha mo re ma t+ai //

NK009(ta)006:737: ming brgya ma la mtshan stong ma //
NK009(ta)006:738: dre'u rta rkang gsum chibs su bcibs //

NK009(ta)006:1126: mdzes pa'i sku la rin chen brgyan //
NK009(ta)006:1127: dar gyi lce'u mu tig dang //
NK009(ta)006:1128: dril bu g.yer kha'i rgyan cha ldan //
NK009(ta)006:1129: sman phran 'bum gyi gtso mo mdzad //
NK009(ta)006:1130: khros pas mi sdug gzugs 'chang zhing //
NK009(ta)006:1131: gcan dang 'phro rgod zhi zhing rdzu //
NK009(ta)006:1132: bran g.yogs 'khor bcas gtor ma longs //
NK009(ta)006:1133: bdag cag rig 'dzin bsgrub pa la //
NK009(ta)006:1134: dgra bgegs gegs dang zor kha langs //
NK009(ta)006:1135: mi mthun phyogs rnams ji snyed pa //
NK009(ta)006:1136: bzlog cing zhi bar mdzad du gsol //
NK009(ta)006:1138: zhes pas mchod la nang du log nas /
NK009(ta)006:1141: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK009(ta)006:1142: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor dang bcas //
NK009(ta)006:1144: shin tu gdug pa'i sems can la //
NK009(ta)006:1145: zhe sdang chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK009(ta)006:1146: skad cig nyid la brlag mdzad dam //
NK009(ta)006:1147: brlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK009(ta)006:1148: brlag mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK009(ta)006:1156: gdon stong phrag brgyad bcu la sogs pa'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad brlag par gyur cig /
NK009(ta)006:1157: de nas tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK009(ta)006:1158: hoh zhal zas tshogs kyi longs spyod la //
NK009(ta)006:1159: bdag dang gzhan du mi dmigs pas //
NK009(ta)006:1160: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas pas //
NK009(ta)006:1161: mnyam sbyor chen po'i dngos grub thob //
NK009(ta)006:1162: a la la hoh zhes blangs te phung khams kyi
NK009(ta)006:1163: lha tshogs zag med bde bas tshim par rol lo
NK009(ta)006:1164: // de nas tshogs kyi lhag ma byin brlabs nas /
NK009(ta)006:1166: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nu yis //
NK009(ta)006:1167: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan btags pa //
NK009(ta)006:1168: lhag ma kha chu'i dam tshig can //
NK009(ta)006:1169: tshul bzhin mchod kyi gshegs su gsol //
NK009(ta)006:1170: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis po //
NK009(ta)006:1171: ye shes las las grub pa mo //
NK009(ta)006:1172: mkha' la thogs med 'gro ba ma //
NK009(ta)006:1173: don la sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK009(ta)006:1174: sgrub pa po la phan gdags phyir //
NK009(ta)006:1175: bran gyi tshul du khas blangs pa //
NK009(ta)006:1176: sngon gyi thugs dam brtser dgongs nas //
NK009(ta)006:1177: lhag ma'i gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK009(ta)006:1178: ma h+aa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:1180: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)006:1181: de nas dngos grub zhu ba ni /
NK009(ta)006:1183: rdo rje phur pa'i lha tshogs dgongs //
NK009(ta)006:1184: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las kyi //
NK009(ta)006:1185: byin rlabs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK009(ta)006:1186: stobs kyis dgra bgegs bsgral ba dang //
NK009(ta)006:1187: sku gsung thugs gsum dngos grub mchog /
NK009(ta)006:1188: dngos grub thams cad dus 'dir stsol //
NK009(ta)006:1189: tshe yi snying po rgyud gsum po //
NK009(ta)006:1190: srog gi snying po gzhal yas khang //
NK009(ta)006:1191: skye shi med pa byang chub sems //
NK009(ta)006:1192: sku gsung thugs la rab tu thob //
NK009(ta)006:1194: a yu pha la sid+d+hi sid+d+hi h'u /
NK009(ta)006:1195: a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah a be sha ya +aah de nas bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK009(ta)006:1196: hoh rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK009(ta)006:1197: thugs rjes bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK009(ta)006:1198: bdag ni so so'i skye bo la //
NK009(ta)006:1199: sems ni nyon mongs dbang gyur pas //
NK009(ta)006:1200: mi dge log pa'i bya ba dang //
NK009(ta)006:1201: bag med bying rgod dbang gyur pas //
NK009(ta)006:1202: ting 'dzin ma gsal rdzas ma tshang //
NK009(ta)006:1203: brjed ngas lhag chad gyur pa yis //
NK009(ta)006:1204: dngos grub rab chad gyur pa gang //
NK009(ta)006:1205: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs par stsol //
NK009(ta)006:1206: yi ge brgya pa brjod do //
NK009(ta)006:1207: de nas rtag chad kyi mtha' gsal ba ni /
NK009(ta)006:1208: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha rnams h'u gsum du gyur /
NK009(ta)006:1209: phata gsum gyi de las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK009(ta)006:1210: don gnyis byas nas h'u gsum la thim /
NK009(ta)006:1211: gnyis po bdag nyid rtsa ba'i h'u la thim /
NK009(ta)006:1212: de yang zhabs kyu nas n+aa da'i tha bar du thim //
NK009(ta)006:1213: n+aa da chos kyi dbyings su thim ste /
NK009(ta)006:1214: rang bzhin sems kyi chos nyid ni //
NK009(ta)006:1215: ma bcos lhug par gnas pa'i don //
NK009(ta)006:1216: rtag chad dngos po'i mtha' spangs shing //
NK009(ta)006:1217: brjod bral mu bzhi las 'das pa //
NK009(ta)006:1218: rtsol med gnas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK009(ta)006:1219: phur pa zhes ni de la bya //
NK009(ta)006:1220: zhes mi rtog par bzhag go //
NK009(ta)006:1222: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i lhar ldang ngo //
NK009(ta)006:1223: spyod pa rgyud kyi dam tshig bzhi bsrung ba ni /
NK009(ta)006:1227: gsang ba'i brda bsrung ba rnams tshul bzhin du nyams 'og tu chud par bya'o //
NK009(ta)006:1228: de nas bkra shis kyi me tog 'thor ro //
NK009(ta)006:1230: tshad med snying rje chen po yis //
NK009(ta)006:1231: srid pa phur bu sgrub pa yi //
NK009(ta)006:1232: srid gsum lha yi 'khor lor dag /
NK009(ta)006:1233: rab 'byams rgyal ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK009(ta)006:1234: rdo rje lus kyi khams gsum po //
NK009(ta)006:1235: srog stsol lam gyis gnad bsnun pas //
NK009(ta)006:1236: bde stong dga' bzhi'i ngo bor dag /
NK009(ta)006:1237: phyag rgya mchog gi m+aa ra bsad pa'i da la ru //
NK009(ta)006:1238: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa btab //
NK009(ta)006:1239: dgra bgegs rmig med rtsa nas dag /
NK009(ta)006:1240: bstan pa rgyas pa'i bkra chos dbyings spros dang bral ba la //
NK009(ta)006:1241: rig pa ye shes mnyam sbyor bas //
NK009(ta)006:1242: rdul bral mkha' ltar rnam par dag /
NK009(ta)006:1243: 'bras bu mchog gi bkra shis shog /
NK009(ta)006:1244: 'di ltar snyan brgyud phur pa la //
NK009(ta)006:1245: 'phyong drug las dang sngags drug gis //
NK009(ta)006:1246: gdab pas phrin las tshang ba 'di //
NK009(ta)006:1247: mchog dbyangs sprul pa gter chen des //
NK009(ta)006:1248: bde skyong mi yi nor bu gsum //
NK009(ta)006:1249: dam tshig rdzas kyi d+aa ma ru //
NK009(ta)006:1250: rtsa ba'i phur sgrom dang bcas kyi //
NK009(ta)006:1251: man+dala phul te gsol btab ngor //
NK009(ta)006:1252: phur pa lcam lugs rgyal po'i lugs //
NK009(ta)006:1253: sna nam lugs dang jo mo'i lugs //
NK009(ta)006:1254: dbye bar grags pa mang na yang //
NK009(ta)006:1255: mtsho rgyal thugs kyi brnag pa'i chos //
NK009(ta)006:1257: zab 'dus tshang bar gnad du bsdus //
NK009(ta)006:1258: lag len gsal bar bgyis pa po //
NK009(ta)006:1260: dge bas bdag dang 'gro ba kun //
NK009(ta)006:1261: byang chub sgrub la bar gcod pa'i //
NK009(ta)006:1262: bdud bzhi'i g.yul las rnam rgyal nas //
NK009(ta)006:1263: rdo rje gzhon nu'i go 'phang gi //
NK009(ta)006:1264: 'bras bu mchog la reg gyur cig /
NK009(ta)006:1265: ces pa'ang yang le mchog sprul rin po che'i bka'
NK009(ta)006:1266: bskul mang du gnang ba'i rkyen gyis smad las dug
NK009(ta)006:1267: phur nag po'i phrin las kyi byang bu 'di 'od
NK009(ta)006:1268: gsal rin chen snying po pad+ma las 'brel rtsal gyis
